"In America students and academics are victims of torture and lynching."> Accusa> coming from Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan, > who commented on police intervention from Ankara. "In some prestigious universities students and academics are protesting against the ongoing massacre. That's why they are victims of torture and violence. Academics and rectors lose their place and are fired as well as students. No one says a word, they just wait for the situation to settle down. We have discovered that it is Israel who sets the limit to the concept of democracy in the West," Erdogan said.
